Package fr.cs.group12.myFoodora.order

Class Order

java.lang.Object
fr.cs.group12.myFoodora.order.Order
public class Order extends Object
This class represents an order in the MyFoodora system. An order contains a customer, a restaurant, a list of menu items, a list of meals, a total price, a courier for delivery, and the time the order was placed.
